title: Chicken Trender Basket 8/25: Messi, Aaliyah, Sean Connery, Katie Porter
itunes:title: Chicken Trender Basket 8/25: Messi, Aaliyah, Sean Connery, Katie Porter
description:
On this edition of the Chicken Trender Basket Jack and Miles discuss Lionel Messi's desire to leave Barcelona after two decades, Aaliyah's catalogue is coming to streaming services, Sean Connery turned 90 today, and Katie Porter exposed Louis Dejoy.
